reviewText:
This game is a disappointing strategy game. The following are the reasons:
-The storyline does not fit other Tom Clancy's level, it only means to start a total war but forgets why;
-The combat is more like a card game, which means that you cannot find any tactics in this game;
-Even though it is published several years ago, it doesn't show any new factors.
Conclusion:
As for now, you'd better purchase Wargame instead:)
